column8: Mostly clear. Winds south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h.

Partly cloudy. Areas of early fog. The chance of thunderstorms with little or no rainfall in the afternoon and evening. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to around 7 with daytime temperatures reaching the low to mid 20s.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers in the afternoon and evening. The chance of thunderstorms in the afternoon and early evening. Winds north to northeasterly 20 to 30 km/h shifting south to southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 12 with daytime temperatures reaching 21 to 27.

Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds south to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 7 with daytime temperatures reaching between 16 and 20.

Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending north to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 8 and 11 with daytime temperatures reaching between 17 and 22.
